                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">–°–æ–∑–¥–∞–Ω–∞:</div>
                    <div class="info-value">@link.CreatedAt.ToString("dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm")</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">IP —Å–æ–∑–¥–∞—Ç–µ–ª—è:</div>
